OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight mist and low
OL,6,Fcloud soon clearing this morning.
OL,7,FOtherwise all parts will have a dry
OL,8,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Very
OL,9,Fwarm, locally hot in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will remain dry and mostly
OL,14,Fclear across all parts. Light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FAny overnight mist soon
OL,17,Fclearing to leave all areas with a dry
OL,18,Fand sunny day. Very warm or hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
